div.p: VOD Cost Model: $X per video processed (one-time) Storage: $Y per GB/month
Live Cost Model: $Z per minute streaming (continuous) Transcoding: $A per stream per minute CDN: $B per GB delivered
Example: 1 hour live stream = $5-10 1000 concurrent viewers = $50-100/hour
